= WebClearFusion -- README =
Description in two languages (ru,en). Technical translation is bad, I speak, so that might meet the description of the error.
Project author:
	Lovepsone (<lovepsone@mail.ru>) and frostzhenya (<sexplay2009@mail.ru>)

Purpose of Project:
	Creating a Web-binding for the server Mangos.

Description of Project:
	The site is divided into two main parts: Main Content and WOW Content.

	Briefly about the parts:

	Main Content contains several subparts: Onovnoy content, Admin, Forum.
	 Its main content - is the main part of the site, in which the heart soderzhitya site: Its main run in the modules and functions, and so on.
	 Admin (Site Control Panel) - designed to manage the news, panels, links, and so on.
	 Forum - is designed for messaging, kokogo clarify something haunting question.

	WOW Content contains the ACP, the data on WOW. This part can be turned off if you want to use a different site themes.
	 ACP (Account Control Panel) - designed to manage the accounts of players and characters.

The project is being tested at the source code of rsa (branch mangosr2) <https://github.com/mangosR2/mangos>
In the future we plan to support the project trynitycore.

Installing the engine:
	read instal.

